div.h1: CPU Exception Flow: Divide Error to Handler
div.p: Complete interrupt path from fault to recovery
ESP [EFLAGS] pushed [CS=0x08] pushed [EIP] pushed [local vars] [return addr]
ESP [Error Code] pushed (bits: P,W/U,Rsvd) [EFLAGS] pushed [CS=0x08] pushed [EIP] pushed
CR2 Register Holds faulting address (Page Fault only) Value: 0xDEADBEEF
Handler Entry (asm) asm isr0: cli push byte 0 ; dummy err push byte 0 ; vector jmp isr_common
Handler Entry (asm) asm isr14: cli push byte 14 ; vector jmp isr_common ; err on stack
Common ISR Stub asm isr_common: pusha ; save all GP push ds/es/fs/gs mov ax, 0x10 mov ds, ax ; kernel seg push esp call c_handler
EXCEPTION: Division by zero Vector: 0 EIP: 0xC0102042 CS: 0x08 EFLAGS: 0x202
PAGE FAULT Faulting addr: 0xDEADBEEF Error code: 0x04 Reason: User access to kernel page EIP: 0x00001234
Restore & Return asm pop gs/fs/es/ds popa add esp, 8 ; err + vec iret ; restore all
IRET Instruction Pops EIP, CS, EFLAGS If RPL(CS)=3: also pops ESP, SS Restores interrupt flag from EFLAGS.IF
